server

Class ServerModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • shared.model.ClientModel
        • server.ServerModel

  • public class ServerModel
extends ClientModel
    Representation of the Model that is cached by the server. This has additional "do" methods that the client model does not have.
